Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去喊少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是客人客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您除了客人就不想些别的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出暗访记者  并给予重点服务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后成功进入排行榜前列
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是让我帮忙  我也什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾客都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情应该是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停靠在9号月台  14时15分  开往森田的列车很快就要发车了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场宴会差不多也要到高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是由新娘的朋友们给我们带来的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  有请
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  个子差不多高到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后头发也理得乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天大概不是乱糟糟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请让我看一下名册吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给椿之间的客人们上过茶点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我请你们去拿一套大号浴袍来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常抱歉  我们马上就去拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茶点就拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她问会场的房间也好什么也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她问这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得说是同级生的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  谢谢你  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  蔬菜我切好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是同级生的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他更详细的情况就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就找不到彻先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法回你短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙的样子  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事…貌似这次还真有事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就为了去找彻先生跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连要怎么找他都没有考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算找到了彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的事情也不知道能不能顺利搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会顺利的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  你以前有过好好考虑完才行动的先例吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不都想办法克服困难一路走来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你要是觉得那是最好的办法而去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会船到桥头自然直的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后也一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  一定会船到桥头自然直的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…  要是我真帮到你了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦  阿孝果然好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能正好在我最消沉的时候打电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  你找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…其实也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在会场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  会场又是在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我到市里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的旅馆果然好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去市里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  咦  阿孝你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像听到些什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝总是好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是会来鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们隔得那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝都来为我鼓劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能继续消沉下去呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我绝对会把彻先生给找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功战胜此次危机！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  要战胜它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可能的话连我的份也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀  阿孝也要战胜它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么危机出现了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  话说菜子负责的桐之间里的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他以前好像也来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我还没在这里工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这本记事本是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着他的女儿讨厌吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去告知一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记事本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  我可以问一下新郎的年龄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  可以告知我新郎的年龄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名册就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要新郎的年龄就好  请告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全多亏了阿…孝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在阿孝的面子上  请和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  回市里的班次是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要等四十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你谢谢你谢谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶什么诶啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的跟你道多少声谢都不够！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到彻先生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  全都多亏了阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你又在搞什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去…去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真是的  当然是喜翠庄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的工作才是关键 必须拿出干劲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  乱成一团真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再跟你发短信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备给月之间的客人进行按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time is money对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  波之间的客人晚餐时间由你作陪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不凑巧  本馆今天已经客满了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头盔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车场的管理员借给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…心想着把彻先生带回去一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难得出席朋友的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么强硬地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那是最佳选择所以才来找我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么信任我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会搞定给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来  要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生说的话好像之前也听谁说过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点稍大的头盔中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种第一次闻到的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生脑袋的气味是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝的脑袋也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听小民说  莲先生有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫岸彻我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  赶快进入工作状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么找到彻先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解释的话就说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里你应该说「没关系  告诉我吧」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  让民子来负责油炸可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去炸天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  做不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止你都在学些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我好像听到有什么开始运作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派上用处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我自己也有做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  不要为这种小事大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…巴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾客都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情应该是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（注：松、竹、梅为料理等级，松为特上等、竹为上等、梅为普通）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本旅馆的特别料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是特别的上等料理…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好放松休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  这边完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  雕刻就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六…七…八…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油声变了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝尝沙丁鱼的天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的油声  记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些温啊  不过作为第一次的料理 这已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你指的是食物么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你来这里做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了来拿天妇罗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着  马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您满意了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总算结束了老板娘不在的漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月之间的顾客要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那两位是暗访记者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能取得好分数了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁是都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经尽力招待了所有顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是分数才是重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  绪花  还有工作要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李就这些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你哦  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你帮忙做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢  您有好好休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  昨天女儿突然说要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太匆忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是工作无论如何都要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这个不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈很好的休息过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一身轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁是记者一点都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情应该是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以能这么努力多亏了阿孝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝一君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天到货的新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到我就虚脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分  亏我那么拼命地找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味呢  这个天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}你一个人不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}回来吧  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄也不会有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
